# "PureBASIC.gitattributes" v1.0 | 2017/12/01 | by Tristano Ajmone.
# ------------------------------------------------------------------------------
# A .gitattributes boilerplate for PureBASIC projects.
# Copy and rename this file as ".gitattributes" into the root of your Git repos.
# ------------------------------------------------------------------------------

# Set Git's default behaviour to text-files autodetection, in case users don't
# have `core.autocrlf` set:

* text=auto

# ==============================================================================
#                    Text Files (EOL Normalization Settings)                    
# ==============================================================================
# Explicitly declare all files that are text and tell Git how to handle EOLs:

## =================
## SOURCE CODE FILES
## =================


## PureBASIC
## ---------
*.pb       text
*.pbi      text
*.pbp      text
*.pbf      text
*.cfg      text

## ASM (Fasm/Yasm)
## ---------------
*.ASM      text
*.INC      text
*.asm      text
*.inc      text

## Win Resource Files
## ------------------
*.rc       text eol=crlf

## Shell scripts
## -------------
*.bat      text eol=crlf
*.com      text eol=crlf
*.sh       text eol=lf
*.ps1      text eol=crlf

## ==================
## MISC. DATA FORMATS
## ==================
*.json     text
*.xml      text
*.xhtml    text
*.yaml     text
*.yml      text

## =================
## WEB-RELATED FILES
## =================
*.htm      text
*.html     text
*.css      text
*.js       text

## ===================
## DOCUMENTATION FILES
## ===================
AUTHORS      text
CHANGELOG    text
CHANGES      text
CONTRIBUTING text
COPYING      text
copyright    text
*COPYRIGHT*  text
INSTALL      text
license      text
