UNLICENSE    text
NEWS         text
readme       text
*README*     text
TODO         text

## ===================
## CONFIGURATION FILES
## ===================
*.cnf          text
*.conf         text
*.config       text
*.ini          text
*.prefs        text
.gitattributes text
.gitconfig     text
.gitignore     text

## ===============
## PLAIN-TEXT DOCS 
## ===============
*.adoc        text
*.asciidoc    text
*.markdown    text
*.md          text
*.txt         text

